      <title>新加坡，香港面临与中国关税战争的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/singapore-hk-face-growth-risks-over-us-tariff-war-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社调查的中位数，经济学家在今年下半年下半年降低了新加坡和香港的增长前景，这是美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的不确定性增加，对中国出口的关税征收了更高的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/singapore-hk-face-growth-risks-over-us-tariff-war-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
