    <item>
      <title>股东推七＆amp;我要与库奇 -  tard互动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/shareholder-pushes-seven-i-to-engage-with-couche-tard-over-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七个股东I Holdings Co.正在向公司施加迫使该公司“更深入地”与Altimentation Couche-Tard Inc.相关的475亿美元购买方法。 7-11商店的运营商说，这是这样做的，并拒绝了Artisan Partners Asset Management Inc.对董事会中利益冲突的主张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/shareholder-pushes-seven-i-to-engage-with-couche-tard-over-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Mar 2025 17:07:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦德市场的特朗普贸易看起来像是一场经济衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/the-bond-market-s-trump-trade-is-looking-like-a-recession-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易者表示，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统的混乱关税推出和联邦劳动力削减的风险，美国经济将停滞不前，威胁要进一步限制增长的步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/the-bond-market-s-trump-trade-is-looking-like-a-recession-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Mar 2025 13:58:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
